      "description": "Xavier enhances his subsequent skills each time his skill hits an enemy hero. (Stage I:) Increases Movement Speed by 50% when subsequent skills hit, decaying over 1.2s. (Stage II:) Width of subsequent skills will be greatly increased. (Stage III:) Skill Cooldown reduced by 4s (12s for the Ultimate). At (Stage III), Xavier enters the (Transcendence) state. (Transcendence:) All of Xavier's skills are enhanced to (Stage III) state for 5s (this duration is extended by 1s each time Xavier's skill hits an enemy).",
